<br>
On zones. There really are no &quot;light&quot; or &quot;dark&quot; zones on Rallos. Things used to be that way, and used to be a lot more senselessly dangerous... things have really calmed down. Mainly because there are now uberguilds, where really there weren't any, and our major PK guilds broke up. So it's still a dangerous place, but mainly for high-levels (high-level conflicts can happen; there was a major &quot;war&quot; a while back, but general cease-fires are the order of the day as of last notice). So I can probably branch into better gear with less risk, now. And where I go to get it is really not an issue. Well, level might be.<br>
<br>
Thanks for the suggestions, and in regards to the Spiny weapons... they look like the usual FS-quality crud, and appear to drop in SD and TS. Should I just swing by the Twilight Sea and shout? Any merchants in that area to hunt for? And so on and so forth.<br>
<br>
Thanks for reminding me about Jagged Bands, Jaikar, I *know* those are cheap. And I'll check the Iceclad quests.<br>
<br>
Incidentally, yes, I'll also be trying to level. Time is such a scant resource, these days... <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showMessage?topicID=1465.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showMessage?topicID=1466.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.emailToFriend?topicID=1459.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.threadControl?topicID=1459.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1459.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1459.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub14.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesteelwarriorthearena">The Arena<option value="thesteelwarriorthebattlefield">The BattleField<option value="thesteelwarriorthebunker">The Bunker<option value="thesteelwarriorthetavern">The Tavern<option value="thesteelwarriorfrm6">The Keep</select></td><td><input type=submit value="Go" class=inputbutton></td></tr></table></form></td></